              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11626803-val-shameless-handmaiden?shelf=0-in-my-library-read">0-in-my-library-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11626803-val-shameless-handmaiden?shelf=liaison-alert">liaison-alert</a>
